  Prerequisites: []
  Description: 'In your youth, you made several pilgrimages to important shrines
    and sacred sites. You might have been a mendicant friar, a seller of religious
    relics (real or fraudulent), or just a simple farmer following the dictates of
    your faith. Whatever the aims of your wanderings now, your faith still protects
    you on the road.

    

    Choose two attribute boosts. One must be to Wisdom
    or Charisma, and one is a free attribute boost.

    

    You''re trained
    in the Religion skill, and the Lore skill for your patron deity. You gain the
    Pilgrim''s Token skill feat.'
